<para>
  <command>OOF.Mesh.Boundary_Conditions.Enable</command> enables a
  previously <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Mesh.Boundary_Conditions.Disable">disabled</link>
  <link linkend="RegisteredClass-BC">boundary condition</link>.  An
  enabled boundary condition will be used when its &mesh; is <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Mesh.Solve">solved</link>, if its &equation;
  and &field; are <link
  linkend="MenuItem-OOF.Mesh.Equation.Activate">active</link>.
</para>

